          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1.Movies dominate the platform, contributing </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>~68%</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> of total content. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2.Content growth accelerated significantly </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>after 2016</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>, indicating rapid expansion.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>.TV-MA and TV-14</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> are the most common ratings, targeting mature audiences. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>4</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>.Drama and International genres</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> are the most frequently produced categories. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>5.Most movies fall within the </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>80–120 minutes</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> duration range .</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>6.Content is globally distributed, with strong contributions from </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>multiple countries.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
